## Strategi Pricing

### Model Freemium

```mermaid
graph LR
    A["🆓 Free Tier"] --> B["⭐ Pro Tier"] --> C["💎 Ultimate Tier"]
    
    A --- A1["Plain text cleaning"]
    A --- A2["5.000 karakter/hari"]
    A --- A3["1 preset aktif"]
    A --- A4["Auto-clear clipboard"]
    
    B --- B1["Semua fitur Fase 1-3"]
    B --- B2["Unlimited usage"]
    B --- B3["Custom presets & rules"]
    B --- B4["History, Snippets, Templates"]
    B --- B5["Format converters"]
    B --- B6["Multi-clipboard & Queue"]
    
    C --- C1["AI features"]
    C --- C2["OCR paste"]
    C --- C3["Cross-device sync"]
    C --- C4["Plugin system"]
```

### Opsi Harga

| Model | Harga | Fitur | Target |
|-------|-------|-------|--------|
| **Free** | Rp 0 | Core cleaning + auto-clear | Pengguna kasual |
| **Pro (Lifetime)** | Rp 150.000 – 250.000 (~$10–15) | Semua fitur Fase 1–3 | Power user, mahasiswa |
| **Pro (Bulanan)** | Rp 15.000 – 45.000 (~$1–3/bulan) | Semua fitur Fase 1–3 | Profesional |
| **Ultimate (Lifetime)** | Rp 350.000 – 500.000 (~$22–30) | Pro + AI + OCR + Sync | Enterprise, heavy user |
| **Ultimate (Bulanan)** | Rp 50.000 – 75.000 (~$3–5/bulan) | Pro + AI + OCR + Sync | Tim & perusahaan |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Harga lifetime direkomendasikan sebagai opsi utama. Ultimate tier mungkin perlu subscription karena cross-device sync memerlukan biaya server.

